
This repository hosts all files and documentation produced for the datarepresentation Project. 
In here, you will find a Flask server file, data access object (DAO) file, configuration template file and a Web page called .

This project is also hosted on the free (pythonanywhere.com) cloud service which can be accessed here.

To run the WEB app, please:
You will need a web browser such as Chrome or Firefox.

Software used in this project:
Visual Studio Code 
Anaconda
MySQL workbench

Download and install Flask from PyPi.
To start the Flask server, a small shell script named (runit) is included to start the server and enable error logging
